&lt;li&gt;Support junior team members through informal mentorship, code review, and knowledge sharing where appropriate.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on industry trends and techniques in marketing analytics, experimentation, and applied data science, and apply them pragmatically to Hone’s context.&lt;/li&gt;
