&lt;li&gt;Contribute to employer branding and candidate experience initiatives that help Hone stand out in the market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help build and refine our recruiting infrastructure as we scale - including process documentation, interview training, and intake frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
